Class CalendarValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.sw.Calendar.CalendarValues

  • public class CalendarValues
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Patrick Griffin - G00314635 This class handles the getters and setters for the users events data. The setters are used in the CalendarEvents to set the user data. The getters are using in the MongoConnection to retrieve data.
